comments: Batum (LAC) brings his hands toward Hunter (ATL) and marginal contact occurs as Batum (LAC) releases away to roll.
Powell (LAC) extends his hand to Young's (ATL) front and initiates contact that affects his SQBR during the drive.  The illegal contact from Powell occurs prior to Young hooking Powell's arm.
Batum (LAC) brings his hands toward Hunter (ATL) and marginal contact occurs as Batum (LAC) releases away to pop.
Young (ATL) brings his arm toward Leonard's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Leonard's (LAC) drive.
Okongwu (ATL) brings both arms toward Zubac (LAC) and initiates contact that impedes his ability to pursue the rebound.
Powell (LAC) brings his arm to Young's (ATL) front monetarily as Young moves through the contact and continues his path to the basket.
Hunter (ATL) is moving alongside Leonard's (LAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during Leonard's (LAC) drive.
Collins (ATL) rotates his body slightly as he goes into the air to contest Leonard's (LAC) driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Okongwu (ATL) establishes himself in Mann's (LAC) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Hunter (ATL) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Okongwu (ATL) and Zubac (LAC) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Morris (LAC) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps prior to releasing his jump shot.
Morris Sr. (LAC) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Murray (ATL) brings both hands to Powell (LAC) and marginal contact occurs as Powell receives the inbound pass.
Leonard (LAC) brings his right hand underneath the ball prior to resuming his dribble.
